game.name: Baby Around The World Australia
game.description:
Hey girls! It is time to play another high-quality and rich features enabled game from the Baby Around the World series. In this free online cooking game for girls, we are much excited to join the most beautiful girl Jessie in her unique and exciting trip to Australia, which is in itself known as a land full of exotic locations and cute little kangaroos. Start her wonderful journey with a brand new cooking recipe in which you would help her to cook popular and extremely tasty cantaloupe sherbet. 

Find everything you need to make your play interesting and electrifying in Baby Around the World Australia. Once it is done, you also have to take care of selecting a cute traveling outfit for her. Make sure that your chosen dress will be enough to make her look fabulous and unique. We hope that you will have great fun while assisting the little girl during her adventurous trip in this brand new kitchen game for girls and boys. She is crazy enough to explore new cultures and the food of a particular region. In the first step, you will have to help her to prepare a delicious Australian dessert. 

Start this recipe with cutting some scrumptious mangoes and blending them with some honey and milk. Then put them in the freezer for a while. Once you are done with its preparation, also decorate it with some tasty strawberries. Then help this cute and little baby to color a fun and exciting Australian landscape that features the extremely beautiful koala. The bottom part of the screen includes various colors for your help. Also, dress her up with a wonderful outfit that is perfect for the continent she is currently in. All the best kids to enjoy a lot in this cute html5 game!
